| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5997 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 67d5fb31-d14a-524e-b8ec-7d0fe19b2241"
